<section class="section section-tight" aria-labelledby="cta-title">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-banner">
      <h2 id="cta-title">¿Listo para <em>aparecer primero</em>?</h2>
      <p>
        Una llamada de 30 minutos, sin compromiso. Te decimos si podemos ayudarte
        y, si no, a quién acudir. Honestidad por delante.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-primary">
          Solicitar propuesta
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+34618015995" class="btn btn-ghost">
          Llamar · 618 015 995
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-banner {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--peach) 0%, var(--accent-soft) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: clamp(44px, 6vw, 72px);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cta-banner::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 60% at 50% 120%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6), transparent);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cta-banner h2 {
    font-family: var(--ff-display);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4.5vw, 60px);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #3D2818;
    text-wrap: balance;
    position: relative;
  }
  .cta-banner h2 em { color: var(--accent-hover); font-style: italic; }
  .cta-banner p {
    color: #5C3D25;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto 32px;
    position: relative;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .cta-banner .cta-row {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .cta-banner :global(.btn-ghost) {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    border-color: rgba(61, 40, 24, 0.25);
    color: #3D2818;
  }
  .cta-banner :global(.btn-ghost:hover) { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6); }
</style>
